(37193, 61569, 3557, 1, '得不到的愛情 UNREQUITED LOVE', '樂觀爽朗的Macy紀錄過去青澀又低潮的時期', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '得不到的愛情	Unrequited Love\r\n曲：姚敏  \r\n詞：嚴寬\r\n\r\n我得不到你的愛情	I cannot win your love\r\n像冬夜裡沒有光明	Like a gloomy winter night\r\n你不給我一顆赤心	You wouldn’t give me your true heart\r\n像黑夜裡頭找不到那蹤影 Like a dark night without a trace\r\n	\r\n我得不到你的愛情	I cannot win your love\r\n像春花沒有雨淋	Like spring flowers without rain\r\n你不給我一顆赤心	You wouldn’t give me a true heart\r\n像夢裡春花留下一點幻影 Like the illusion of flowers in a dream\r\n	\r\n我要你的愛情	I want your love\r\n我要你的赤心	I want your true love\r\n你不給我溫馨	You don’t give me affection\r\n何處有熱情去找尋	So where is the passion?\r\n	\r\n像黑夜裡頭找不到那蹤影	Like a dark night without a trace\r\n因為我得不到得不到你的愛情	Because I cannot, cannot win your love\r\n像夢裡春花下一點幻影	                     Like the illusion of flowers in a dream\r\n因為我想得到想得到你的愛情	Because I want to, want to win your love\r\n	\r\n\r\n', '', 325, '', '姚敏', '嚴寬', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 11:51:58', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
