(37196, 61569, 3557, 2, '夢裡相思 LANGUISHING DREAMS', 'Macy送給逝去外婆，遙念在美無法送外婆最後一程的心聲', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '夢裡相思	Languishing Dreams\r\n詞：姚炎\r\n曲：王福齡\r\n\r\n你在哪裡  	Where are you?\r\n看也看不到  	I look but cannot see (you)\r\n摸也摸不著	I reach but cannot feel (you)\r\n你曾真實的到過這裡	Once you were truly here\r\n如今你離我遠去	Now you have left me and gone far away\r\n既然生命的來去 由不得你	Since life is beyond your control\r\n只盼在夢裡在夢裡見到你	I only hope to see you in my dreams\r\n	\r\n我有訴不盡的情意	I am filled with countless sentiment\r\n每晚在夢裡呼喚你	Every night in my dreams I call for you\r\n我倆千山萬水分離	We stand worlds apart\r\n兩地相思夢牽繫	We miss each other deeply\r\n	\r\n我有訴不盡的悲悽	I am filled with endless sorrow\r\n寄託在夢裡帶給你	Through dreams I bring them to you\r\n雖然千山萬水隔離	Even though we are worlds apart\r\n但願在夢裡相依	I only wish to embrace you in my dreams\r\n	\r\n夜月淒寒靜靜徘徊	The moon paces silently in the cold and dreary night\r\n徘徊在小橋樓台	Pacing from bridge to balcony\r\n景色依舊良辰不在	The scene remains but the moment has passed\r\n人兒你幾時回來	Dear, when will you return?\r\n	\r\n我有訴不盡的悲悽	I am filled with endless sorrow\r\n寄託在夢裡帶給你	Through dreams I bring them to you\r\n雖然千山萬水隔離	Even though we are worlds apart\r\n但願在夢裡相依	I only wish to embrace you in my dreams\r\n	\r\n我有訴不盡的情意	I am filled with countless sentiment\r\n', '', 426, '', '王福齡', '姚炎', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 11:55:14', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
