(37199, 61569, 3557, 3, '天涯歌女 THE WANDERING SONGSTRESS', '從台灣出走到美國繼續音樂的旅程，老公無怨無悔的全力支持，Macy用這首歌傾訴自己的際遇', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '天涯歌女	The Wandering Songstress\r\n詞: 田漢 \r\n曲: 賀綠汀\r\n\r\n天涯呀海角　覓呀覓知音 To the ends of the earth, seeking a confidant\r\n小妹妹唱歌郎奏琴	Where his music will compliment her voice\r\n郎呀咱們倆是一條心	We are two but our hearts are one\r\n哎呀　哎呀　郎呀咱們倆是一條心	Aiya aiya our hearts are one\r\n	\r\n家山呀北望　淚呀淚沾襟  Gazing north towards home as tears wet her sleeve\r\n小妹妹想郎直到今	She longed for him till this day\r\n郎呀患難之交恩愛深	Adversity makes for deeper love\r\n哎呀　哎呀　郎呀患難之交恩愛深	Aiya aiya adversity makes for deeper love\r\n	\r\n人生呀誰不　惜呀惜青春  In life, alas, who doesn’t cherish youth?\r\n	\r\n小妹妹似線郎似針	She is thread he is a needle\r\n郎呀穿在一起不離分	Threaded through and undivided\r\n哎呀　哎呀　郎呀穿在一起不離分	Aiya aiya threaded through and undivided\r\n	', '', 348, '', '賀綠汀', '田漢 ', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 11:57:49', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
