(37201, 61569, 3557, 4, '我唯一的愛 MY ONLY LOVE', '用這首歌獻給最深愛的老公，感謝一路走來的扶持與呵護', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '我唯一的愛	My Only Love\r\n詞曲：MELLIN ROBERT,WOOD GUY\r\n改編詞：MACY CHEN\r\n\r\n你的愛就像音樂擁抱著我	Your love embraces me like music\r\n像春天的微風 輕拂我的胸口	Like a spring breeze across my chest\r\n你給了我真愛的力量	You gave me the power of true love\r\nMy one and only love	My one and only love\r\n	\r\n當神秘夜色籠罩漆黑大地	As mysterious night falls dark across the land\r\n你是唯一的光明	You are the only shining light\r\n當我們擁抱在一起	When we embrace\r\n你的吻是那麼的甜蜜	Your kiss is ever so sweet\r\nMy one and only love	My one and only love\r\n	\r\n和你在一起 像在天堂	Being with you is like being in heaven\r\n是我從沒到過的地方	A place I have never been\r\n你溫暖的雙唇給我纏綿的溫存	Your warm lips give me lingering tenderness\r\n我知道你是唯一的愛人	I know you are my only love\r\n	\r\n從沒有一個人能讓我瘋狂	Never has anyone made me this crazy\r\n那深深的感動觸動我的靈魂	This intensity deeply moves my soul\r\n我肯定你是我的唯一	I am certain you are my one and only\r\nMy one and only love	My one and only love\r\n	', '', 396, '', 'MACY CHEN', 'MELLIN ROBERT,WOOD GUY', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:00:58', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37202, 61569, 3557, 5, '哈林幻想曲 HARLEM FANTASIA', 'Macy選用「Caravan」和「Harlem Nocturne」這兩首曲子，融合一起改編成「Harlem Fantasia」，靈感來自於哈林區表演的感受，中西合璧的詮釋，呈現全新的爵士精神', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '哈林狂想曲	Harlem Fantasia\r\n(mix with HARLEM NOCTURNE and CARAVAN)\r\nHARLEM NOCTURNE--\r\n詞曲:DICK ROGERS , EARLE HAGEN   CARAVAN--\r\n詞曲:DICK ROGERS , EARLE HAGEN \r\n改編詞：Macy Chen\r\n\r\nDeep music fills the night	Deep music fills the night\r\nDeep in the heart of Harlem	Deep in the heart of Harlem\r\nAnd tho’ the stars are bright	And tho’ the stars are bright\r\nthe darkness is taunting me	the darkness is taunting me\r\n	\r\nOh what a sad refrain	Oh what a sad refrain\r\nA nocturne born in Harlem	A nocturne born in Harlem\r\nThat melancholy strain 	That melancholy strain\r\nForever is haunting me	Forever is haunting me\r\n	\r\n夜 的哈林充滿了神秘	The Harlem night is filled with mystery\r\n有一點危險和詭異	A little dangerous and a little strange\r\nDuke Ellington 飄來幻影	Duke Ellington’s apparition floats on by\r\n	\r\n音樂 燃燒Apollo戲院裡	Music ignites in the Apollo theater\r\n爵士的音樂唱不停	The symphony of jazz unstoppable\r\n哼一首哈林小夜曲	Humming a Harlem nocturne\r\n	\r\n夜 是多麼瑰麗	Nights -- so exotic\r\n你 是那麼熱情	You -- so passionate\r\n我 醉倒你懷裡	I fall intoxicated into your arms\r\n直到掌聲響起	Until the applause resounds \r\n	\r\n喔 我 就愛這樣沉淪下去	Oh, I just love to keep falling like this\r\n別叫醒我在幻夢裡	Don’t wake me from this fantasy\r\n爵士的靈魂在哈林	The soul of jazz lives in Harlem\r\n	', '', 406, '', 'DUKE ELLINGTON , JUAN TIZOL / Earle Hagen/Dick Rogers', 'DUKE ELLINGTON , JUAN TIZOL / Earle Hagen/Dick Rogers', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:03:57', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37203, 61569, 3557, 6, '蘇州夜曲 SUZHOU NOCTURNE', '改編自李香蘭的「蘇州夜曲」，用爵士樂重新詮釋更有韻味，透過Macy沉穩優雅的嗓音，彷彿身歷蘇州河畔沉醉其美景與音樂之中', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '蘇州夜曲	Suzhou Nocturne\r\n詞：HATTORI RYOICHI\r\n曲 ：HATTORI RYOICHI\r\n\r\n投君懷抱裡	Falling into his arms\r\n無限纏綿意	His affection lasts forever\r\n船歌似春夢	Music chiming dreams of spring\r\n流鶯婉轉啼	Birds are singing\r\n水鄉蘇州	Rivers and lakes surround Suzhou\r\n花落春去	Flowers wilt as spring departs\r\n惜相思長堤	Reminiscing days along the lake shore \r\n細柳依依	Hugging ever so tightly\r\n	\r\n落花順水流 	Petals flow along the river\r\n流水長悠悠	The river shore long and turned\r\n明日漂何處	Where will it take us tomorrow\r\n問君還知否	Does he know or not\r\n倒映雙影	Reflection of the lovers in the water\r\n半喜半羞	Elated but shy\r\n願與卿熱情	Wishing our love and affection\r\n永存長留	Will last forever\r\n', '', 251, '', 'HATTORI RYOICHI', 'HATTORI RYOICHI', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:05:56', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37204, 61569, 3557, 7, '瘋狂的周末 CRAZY WEEKEND', '初到紐約的Macy見證了城市的熱情與活力，將歌詞改編成自己親身體驗的紐約生活與瘋狂', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '瘋狂的周末	Crazy Weekend\r\n詞：楊易文 \r\n曲：姚敏\r\n第二段新增歌詞：MACY CHEN\r\n\r\n禮拜一大家起身太早	Monday everyone gets up too early\r\n禮拜二生意買賣太好	Tuesday business is really good\r\n禮拜三偷偷摸摸打電話	Wednesday I call my darling\r\n哈囉 Darling給我支票	Hello Kenny cut me a check!\r\n	\r\n禮拜四整天伸著懶腰	Thursday stretch and yawn all day\r\n禮拜五看場電影吃個飽	Friday catch a movie and dinner\r\n禮拜六下午跑馬贏了錢	Saturday afternoon win at the racetrack\r\n再排節目玩通宵	And then plan to party the night away\r\n	\r\n酒醉三分興緻好	A little buzzed and feeling good\r\n隨著音樂擺又搖	Swinging with the music to and fro\r\n恰恰恰  Rock & Roll	Cha cha cha rock ‘n roll\r\n越瘋狂越是美妙	Wilder it gets the better it is\r\n	\r\n你不妨自由自在逍遙	Might as well free yourself\r\n你不妨痛痛快快歡笑	Might as well party and laugh out loud\r\n享受這瘋狂週末好時光	Enjoy this crazy weekend’s good times\r\n明天禮拜再睡覺	Tomorrow is Sunday, I’ll sleep late\r\n	\r\n禮拜一我待在家裡哪裡都不去	Monday I stay home and go nowhere\r\n禮拜二教學生怎麼發聲練習	Tuesday I teach students to sing\r\n禮拜三看Rachel生的混血baby	Wednesday I visit Rachel’s newborn baby\r\n哈囉 Lovell  It’s Macy阿姨	Hello Lovell, it’s Auntie Macy\r\n	\r\n禮拜四一大群人去看Yankees	Thursday we go to the Yankee game\r\n禮拜五我終於聽到Diane Reeves	Friday I finally get to hear Diane Reeves\r\n禮拜六下午開車離開City	Saturday afternoon get out of the city\r\n和Darling去和 B Band Jamming	To jam with my darling and the B-Band\r\n	\r\nJamming的地點在森林裡	The jam is in the woods\r\n滿天的星星亮晶晶	A sky full of twinkling stars\r\n恰恰恰 Rock & Roll	Cha cha cha rock ‘n roll\r\n夜越黑音樂越High	Night grows darker and the music gets high\r\n	\r\n紐約的生活快得嚇死你	Life in New York such a fast pace\r\n不穿球鞋怕走路來不及	You can’t keep up without sneakers\r\n享受這隨遇而安的心情	Enjoy whatever comes my way\r\n明天早起慢跑去	Tomorrow get up early for a jog\r\n	\r\n這就是我的生活日記	This is the journal of my life\r\n', '', 238, '', '姚敏', '楊易文 / 第二段新增歌詞：MACY CHEN', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:07:42', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37205, 61569, 3557, 8, '懷念 REMINSCE', '用白光的「懷念」悼念未曾見過面卻有著相同靈魂與生命經歷的外公', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '懷念	Reminisce\r\n詞: 葉逸芳\r\n曲: 陳瑞楨\r\n青紗外   月隱隱	Outside the moon is obscured\r\n青紗內   冷清清	Inside desolation fills the air\r\n琴聲揚   破寂岑	Music breaks the silence\r\n深深打動了我的心	Touch my soul deeply\r\n	\r\n想起了他勾起了情	The memory of him sparks burning emotions\r\n還深深留著他的唇印	His kiss eternal\r\n	\r\n到如今   人兒呀	Today this person\r\n天涯何處去找尋	Is nowhere to be found\r\n忘了吧   鼻兒已酸	Let it all go, forget it all\r\n淚珠兒濕透衣襟	My tears running down\r\n', '', 380, '', '陳瑞楨', '葉逸芳', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:10:45', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37206, 61569, 3557, 9, '出走的決定 FLY AWAY', 'Macy因為對音樂的堅持而決心出走異鄉尋求更高的殿堂，卻在追尋外公的音樂記錄時發現兩人生命經歷竟是如此雷同，於是用這首歌註記相隔75年的共同決定', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '出走的決定	Fly Away \r\n詞: MACY CHEN\r\n曲: MACY CHEN\r\n\r\n感覺變得麻木	Emotions numbing\r\n總覺得好無助	Feeling so helpless\r\n過去那個愛笑的我	Once I loved to smile\r\n現在我只想哭	Now I only feel like crying\r\n我到底怎麼了	What’s happened to me?\r\n無法快樂起來	I can no longer be happy\r\n假裝我自己不在乎	Pretending that I don’t care\r\n但其實很痛苦	When it’s hurting inside\r\n	\r\n我的心啊轉啊轉啊轉個不停	Around and around my heart is spinning\r\n像那風鈴在狂風裡響不停	Like wind chimes thrashing in the wind\r\n有誰能夠指引我去哪裡	Who can point me in the right direction?\r\n那顆心才會平靜	So my heart would find peace?\r\n	\r\n我的心啊轉啊轉啊要轉去哪裡	Around and around where is my heart turning?\r\n我渴望做一些從未做過的事情	I long to do things I’ve never done before\r\n春天的腳步就要來臨	Spring’s footsteps are coming near\r\n我決定出走去	And I’ve decided to step out\r\n	\r\n就算前方的路不平靜	Even if the future is rocky\r\n我也會勇敢往前去	I’d keep going on courageously\r\n春夏秋冬四季不停息	The seasons never take a rest\r\n沒有理由再停留原地	There’s no reason not to move on\r\n	\r\n在我面前如今又是不同的風景	Things are all different now\r\n酸甜苦辣都有不同的意境	Every flavor has a different state of being\r\n雖然走過痛苦辛酸的記憶	Though I’ve been through the pain and heartache\r\n那都是生活的點滴	Those are all bits and pieces of life\r\n沒有痛苦哪有甜蜜	Without the bitter, there is no sweet\r\n沒有失去哪懂珍惜	Without loss, who’d know what to cherish\r\n這就是人生的意義	That’s the meaning of life\r\n喔 我感謝自己的決定	Oh I thank myself for this decision\r\n	\r\n喔 我感謝自己 感謝你和我 Oh I thank myself and thank you\r\n感謝你給我的勇氣	Thank you for the courage you have given me\r\n', '', 393, '', 'MACY CHEN', 'MACY CHEN', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:15:46', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37207, 61569, 3557, 10, ' 晚安我的愛 GOOD NIGHT MY LOVE', '感謝每一位支持Macy的朋友，在聆聽完這張用生命的腳步譜成的華語爵士經典後，祝福大家有個美好的夜晚', '2011-04-29 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 15, '晚安  我的愛	Goodnight, My Love\r\n詞: MACY CHEN\r\n曲: MACY CHEN\r\n\r\n晚安  我的愛	Goodnight, my love\r\n今夜的星光已黯淡	Tonight the stars have faded\r\n我們就在此Say good bye	Let’s just say good bye here\r\n好嗎	Alright?\r\n	\r\n晚安  我的愛	Goodnight, my love\r\n甜蜜的感覺仍然在	The sweetness lingers\r\n今夜就等你入夢來	Tonight I wait for you in my dreams\r\nGood night	Goodnight\r\n	\r\n認識你 到現在 	Since knowing you,\r\n每一分每一秒都覺得精采	every moment has been breathtaking\r\n想和你 一輩子 到永遠	I want to be with you for eternity\r\n讓所有真心相待永遠不會再受傷害	May all sincere waiting never end in pain\r\n	\r\n晚安  我的愛 	Goodnight, my love\r\n今夜的星光已黯淡	Tonight the stars have faded\r\n我們就在此Say good night	Let’s just say goodnight here\r\n晚安	Goodnight\r\n', '', 315, '', 'MACY CHEN', 'MACY CHEN', '', 'SeedMusic ', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-07-15 12:18:14', '2015-03-12 13:47:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
